				<p>Posted by <a href="http://ourlifeinfood.com/author/carrie406/" title="Posts by Carrie" rel="author">Carrie</a> on June 30, 2011 in <a href="http://en.wordpress.com/tag/beef/" title="View all posts in Beef" rel="category tag">Beef</a>, <a href="http://en.wordpress.com/tag/meats/" title="View all posts in Meats" rel="category tag">Meats</a></p>
