				<p>Posted by <a href="http://ourlifeinfood.com/author/carrie406/" title="Posts by Carrie" rel="author">Carrie</a> on June 21, 2011 in <a href="http://en.wordpress.com/tag/beans/" title="View all posts in Beans" rel="category tag">Beans</a>, <a href="http://en.wordpress.com/tag/sausage/" title="View all posts in Sausage" rel="category tag">Sausage</a></p>
